									<children>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[BUTLER] Explodes in gore...replaced by the Avatar of Bhaal., [BHAAL] Explodes out of the Butler.&lt;CodyM&gt;" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="Attitude" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Default" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The butler levitates, held up in the air like a broken marionette on invisible strings. Daggers manifest in the air around him and plunge into his body, making a gory pincusion of him. His mutilated corpse crashes to the ground, and the blood that runs from it forms a dark pool.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;A light glows within the pool, and within the reflection, we see the Bhaal Temple - the eyes of the skull light with flame within the reflection, and a figure moves out of the darkness toward the surface of the pool, where it connects to reality. It is the butler, his hat gone, the flesh peeled back from his skull in places. Thoroughly mutilated and disfigured. His eyes burn with unholy fire - he has become an Avatar of Bhaal." />
										</node>
