			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="0) Start with Dark Urge Origin.&#xD;&#xA;1) With the debugbook, go to Act 3 -&gt; Undercity -&gt; Bhaal Temple -&gt; Bhaal Temple Bridge.&#xD;&#xA;2) Defeat Orin." />
			<attribute id="autoFidelity" type="LSString" value="Gold" />
