			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Orin, Chosen of Bhaal, has died by the DarkUrge's/party's hands.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;If the DU deafted Orin, Bhaal will celebrate his new Chosen and force a decision on them - accept him, or he will reclaim his blood from them.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;If the player was defeated, the player sees a linear scene where Bhaal inflicts his blood on them, leaving them with the urge to kill, but not his slayer powers." />
